lti / listtimer               Lists timers

   Format:
      ;lti
               Lists all timers belonging to current profiles
      ;lti -w
               Lists all timers associated with the current world
      ;lti -g
               Lists all timers associated with the current guild
      ;lti -r
               Lists all timers associated with the current race
      ;lti -c
               Lists all timers associated with the current character
      ;lti -x <category>
               Lists all timers belonging to the current custom profile derived
                  from the category (template) <category>
      ;lti -d <prof>
               Lists all timers belonging to the profile <prof>
      ;lti -i
               Lists all active timer interfaces

   User commands:
      lti / listti / listtimer
